To build
$make

To launch chat application
$sudo ./chat

Send 4KB data
$sudo ./send_4k (note that receive_4k should be run before this)

Send 2MB data
$sudo ./send_2m (note that receive_2m should be run before this)

Send 1GB data
$sudo ./send_1g (note that receive_1g should be run before this)

Argument
You can pass an argument of character to be sent.
For example, if you want to send 2MB of characters of 'G',
$sudo ./send_2m G

If there is no argument passed, it sends 'A' as default.
